reviews.review_text:
Epic run These late 80’s (into Spring of 90) shows are under rated by many. It was a big, bright, tight period for the band. This run at Alpine is superb. Hard to find better quality recording- thanks Charlie!
You’ve almost got to go back to 77 to hear them sound better. The spokes on that wheel are all spinning in unison. Ya know? Love
